      "content": "hey so im 20 weeks pregnant and my sinuses are like super clogged and hurting so bad i cant even sleep. i have some ciprofloxacin left over from a previous infection, would it be okay to take a few of those to clear this up? or is there a specific dose of sudafed i should stick to so it doesnt mess with the baby?",
